{"tid":1453223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫幫手，想搵條片救社工","createTime":"2019-08-12T03:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T07:11:59.000Z","uid":296888,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ea6b97da57a3f8bf04dffcb5cc47f75b40b714b5","tid":1453223,"uid":296888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:34:56.000Z","msg":"我幫手做轉發，希望大家幫幫手救下呢位社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(以下係當事人的呼籲)<br />\n如果大家有8月11日美麗華對出被捕情況的片段，有任何截圖/link請你send比我，因為當時我身邊被防暴警察按在地上被捕的的是社工。<br />\n<br />\n我極需要搵返當時的影片做證據，證明該位同工係沒有任何衝擊行為並且走在行人路上，求求大家幫忙。如認識傳媒的同工也請幫幫手，當時好多記者影住我拎社工證同身邊被防暴制服的社工，我地真係好需要搵返段片。<br />\n<br />\n請大家幫忙協助，我和他也只是幫忙在現場維持秩序疏散，我們也只是盡自己一點棉力，換來的是他被捕。<br />\n<br />\n時間：around 2030 - 2045 美麗華商場對出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b589e510340254574bc75c7dcace70f1e088ce","tid":1453223,"uid":296888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:39:18.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，大家幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90dec055bf661136fd962feb326b7cb485d7d75a","tid":1453223,"uid":287051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:41:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9142e611f5a5b11844816686f5a250be91b91570","tid":1453223,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:42:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"848d29b295b72413b195655d4d53df96fb9f0ff1","tid":1453223,"uid":296888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:44:08.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇到呢個post仲要係社工ge你，麻煩你地都一齊share 俾更多人知呢單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，今次救唔到，你地下次出去就更難做到保護ge角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d60d2ab9862fa8bf26c1268dc27a15f62e44cea","tid":1453223,"uid":148824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:44:31.000Z","msg":"急！禍必及妻兒！犬妻犬兒報料捉發完夢既手足！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1446733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1446733</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8ba32539ad411ddcf2d4665dd4605b14f2350a75","tid":1453223,"uid":296888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:55:45.000Z","msg":"幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85766c37f70d2271c259f88d79cbce6f6ef30a71","tid":1453223,"uid":77524,"like":0,"dislike":0