知道d 9有病ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:15:46.000Z","msg":"諗法正確"},{"pid":"2d9c24ec09e2e265b220e33d57fa056046aa128d","tid":1453223,"uid":172139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:17:38.000Z","msg":"推左先👊🏽<br />\n有冇社工可以幫手share"},{"pid":"aced36e7ef6cc865d1fce9e3c1a285bb0334ce8a","tid":1453223,"uid":122551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:20:16.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"013d30210fda1d67c2492b2a58491d45932ac727","tid":1453223,"uid":276633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:20:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"378483b7a3c35e1d383411d907b93493a783364d","tid":1453223,"uid":247994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:21:43.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"8b03ba889032f597dbca7f512ac672161dfb3f7b","tid":1453223,"uid":296888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2faf3d38db40f7dcda3abb6c9ddfa7bae740a6e","tid":1453223,"uid":169665,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:02:24.000Z","msg":"舉證責任永遠係警方<br />\n高度提防警方索料<br />\n留低律師名同案件號碼<br />\n所有證據只會比律師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:23:28.000Z","msg":"舉證責任永遠係警方（我同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我地個社會本應係咁，但而家班9 係老屈證據，尋晚大家有眼見，佢地查贓嫁禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我個朋友想搵d證據證明自己都係唔信得過d 9姐）<br />\n高度提防警方索料（小心行事我同意，特別係呢個咁敏感ge 時候，但呢段呼籲可以係fb 搵到，佢真係好擔心）<br />\n留低律師名同案件號碼（留係度就真危險，d 9一樣睇到）<br />\n所有證據只會比律師（呢樣如果要咁做無可厚非）"},{"pid":"7856de7d9284e8f7992c6166294403fb75fbd2bb","tid":1453223,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:28:58.000Z","msg":"重新整理<br />\n<br />\n<strong>前線良心記者<br />\n求你哋連成一線，接力問落去<br />\n畀佢哋遊走咗，下一位就follow up question繼續問<br />\n呢啲係我哋最關心嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n每日無論邊個問先，頭幾條都要係呢幾條！！<br />\n每一次問都數， 呢條問題係第幾次第幾日問，未有答案！ 幾時先會有答案？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">請準備好每條問題嘅影片及圖片<br />\n準備播放器，迫使cctvb要播<br />\n佢一路拒絕播嘅畫面出街</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 721點解唔執法？點解只告非法集會？點解全部未落charge？<br />\n播圖播片<br />\n指揮官喺村公所同白衣人對話，當時佢哋手持武器， 點解唔執法？<br />\n播片<br />\n<br />\n2 有證據顯示警方用過期Tear Gas?用咗幾多?點解用?<br />\n請準備圖及片<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n過期催淚彈 成分變質變山埃， 警方會否道歉及賠償？<br />\n<br />\n3. 警察係咪扮示威者，然後執法？ 點解用咁嘅策略 ？ 點證明 冇掉磚？冇煽動？冇放火？會否Charge佢哋參與暴動?<br />\n準備圖及片<br />\n<br />\n4. 點解會係地鐵站 內放催淚彈同胡椒彈？目的係驅趕定拘捕？<br />\n準備片<br />\nFollow up questions<br />\n如果係驅趕，佢哋已經喺地鐵站走緊！ 點解仲要放？ 如果係拘捕，你應該衝入去拉人而唔係放催淚彈胡椒彈！可唔可以解釋下<br />\n<strong>預設答案：</strong>情況混亂，個別事件<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n警察冇專業訓練處理混亂情況？<br />\n個別例子係合理解釋？殺人放火強姦都係個別例子！ 示威者都係混亂情況下先做出唔尋常，唔理智行為，警方接唔接受呢個解釋唔落charge？<br />\n<br />\n5. 有片影到警察放武器入示威者背囊，點解？係唔係插贓嫁禍？<br />\n<strong>預設答案&nbsp;：</strong>&nbsp;冇資料<br />\n預備嗰條片， 講埋時間地點<br />\n叫佢解釋！<br />\n<br />\n6. 太古零距離開槍， 做法是否恰當？咩原因同情況下要咁做？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n7. 北角警察無視白衣人攻擊黑衣人及記者， 荃灣白衣人 一離場，場警察就進場，又係一個巧合？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n一齊畀意見！！<br />\n葵芳地鐵站內放催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchishing87%2Fvideos%2F10156292523426674%2F&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=087b35f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/</a><br />\n<br />\n追打並推落扶手電梯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2196364073824126&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=35d26a42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126</a><br />\n<br />\n太古站開槍 1米內射示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F2424996360930416&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=a81b0311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416</a><br />\n<br />\n竹支嫁禍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424974427599276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F2424974427599276&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=e6f122c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424974427599276</a><br />\n<br />\n唔回應是否扮示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196515767142290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2196515767142290&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=7448f0e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196515767142290</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者會共識<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449180</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n求大家將呢段散去所以唔同post，代推文<br />\n<br />\n一定要畀記者知<br />\n佢哋係我哋唯一嘅槍口，可以直接質問黑警同政府"},{"pid":"cbb8f2f6e828fbdc91758dc9c46da0493c285772","tid":1453223,"uid":130792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19fe6e004efdb33a43f5a2e3073670787f281bac","tid":1453223,"uid":128522,"like":1,"dis